&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Know about Jammu and Kashmir:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Capital&lt;/strong&gt;: Srinagar (Summer), Jammu (Winter).&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Official Language&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;strong&gt;Urdu&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Regional Festivals: &lt;/span&gt;
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;Hemis festival &amp;ndash; a Buddhist festival of Ladakh.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;Urs also is known as Ziarats &amp;ndash; a Kashmiri Muslim festival.&lt;/li&gt;
